WEBVTT

00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:32.176
for a company to discriminate
against hiring an employee

00:05:32.200 --> 00:05:35.280
based on if she or he wears dreadlocks.

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:37.776
In the case,

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:40.056
the hiring manager in Mobile, Alabama

00:05:40.080 --> 00:05:41.800
is on record as saying,

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:44.800
"I'm not saying yours are messy,

00:05:45.640 --> 00:05:46.976
but ...

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:48.572
you know what I'm talking about."

00:05:50.440 --> 00:05:52.680
Well, what was she talking about?

00:05:53.760 --> 00:05:55.480
Did she think that they were ugly?

00:05:56.920 --> 00:06:01.376
Or maybe they were
just a little too Afrocentric